Maintainer: Jeffrey C. Oliver <jcoliver@email.arizona.edu>
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Description: Provides functions for calculating several summary statistics for 
    rainfall and temperature data. Uses daily site data to calculate values for 
    annual, user-defined seasons.
